title: How do I get the new Pixel 3a if I'm from Denmark? It's not for sale here yet.
content: Google has revealed the new Pixel 3a, and I'm interested in getting one. The problem is just that it's not for sale in Denmark yet. Will I have to order it from a different country, or do I just wait till I can get it here in Denmark? And if so, how long will that take?
